00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:18.619
<v Speaker 1>Deber.

00:00:18.619 --> 00:00:23.500
<v Speaker 1>And would must or would o gives us the meaning should

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:26.560
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:00:26.560 --> 00:00:30.080
<v Speaker 1>There should be something to it.

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:33.280
<v Speaker 1>Good.

