<v Speaker 1>What is later or more late?

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:32.920
<v Speaker 1>Good.

00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:36.440
<v Speaker 1>And what is the root for the mood tense of go?

00:02:36.440 --> 00:02:38.200
<v Speaker 1>Boy ba becomes

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:40.560
<v Speaker 2>Vaya.

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:41.360
<v Speaker 1>Good.

